{
  "title": "Mildly Savory Argentinian Onion Stir fry",
  "description": "A savory and velvety Argentinian dish featuring yellow onion, this stir fry is a light and keto-friendly option for a quick meal. It combines the flavors of Argentina with the simplicity of a stir fry.",
